1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,490
Ask yourself every day, what can I do today to make my wife and family happy?

2
00:00:06,561 --> 00:00:11,171
This may seem almost too simple, but it is amazingly effective.

3
00:00:11,440 --> 00:00:19,410
One evening, as part of a sales training program, I was discussing building the home environment for selling success.

4
00:00:19,680 --> 00:00:25,890
To illustrate a point, I asked the salesmen, who were all married, when was the last time,

5
00:00:26,001 --> 00:00:33,010
aside from Christmas, your wedding anniversary, or her birthday, that you surprised your wife with a special gift?

6
00:00:33,601 --> 00:00:35,970
Even I was shocked at the answers.

7
00:00:36,081 --> 00:00:41,651
Of the thirty-five salesmen, only one had surprised his wife in the past month.

8
00:00:41,920 --> 00:00:49,010
Many of the group answered, between three and six months, and over a third said, I can't remember.

9
00:00:49,360 --> 00:00:50,369
Imagine!

10
00:00:50,561 --> 00:00:56,530
And some men wonder why their wives no longer treat them like Mr. King with a crown.

11
00:00:57,440 --> 00:01:01,970
I wanted to impress these salesmen with the power of the thoughtful gift.

12
00:01:02,160 --> 00:01:07,890
The next evening, I arranged to have a florist appear just before the close of the session.

13
00:01:08,160 --> 00:01:10,691
I introduced him and leveled with them.

14
00:01:10,960 --> 00:01:17,890
I want each of you to discover what a little unexpected remembrance will do to build a better home environment.

15
00:01:18,160 --> 00:01:21,651
I've arranged with the florist for each of you to get a fine,

16
00:01:21,680 --> 00:01:25,010
long-stemmed red rose for just fifty cents.

17
00:01:25,200 --> 00:01:29,970
Now, if you don't have fifty cents, or if you think your wife isn't worth that,

18
00:01:29,970 --> 00:01:33,490
" they laughed, "'I'll buy the flower for her myself.

19
00:01:33,760 --> 00:01:39,811
All I ask is that you take the rose to your wife, and then tomorrow evening tell us what happened.

20
00:01:40,400 --> 00:01:47,090
Don't, of course, tell her how you came to purchase this rose for her." They understood.

21
00:01:47,440 --> 00:01:55,410
Without exception, every fellow testified the next evening that the mere investment of 50 cents had made his wife happy.

